      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-6 border-b">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-4">
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 px-4 py-6 mb-4 md:mb-0 border-r padding-body" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-duration="2000">
            <p class="text-xl mb-3" style={{ color: '#ff3c00' }}>WHY CHOOSE US?</p>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 test">Start your project with the best contractors in your region.</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 px-4 pt-2 padding-body" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="2000">
            <p class="ml-0 md:ml-6 font-body pb-4">
              K-Constructions is a renowned construction company, known for its commitment to excellence and quality. Founded on principles of sustainability,
              innovation, and reliability, our company has built a solid reputation in the field of residential, commercial, and industrial construction.
              <br><br>
              With a team of highly skilled experts, K-Constructions offers a comprehensive range of services, from architectural design to the completion of turnkey projects.
            </p>
            <a href="about" class="btn btn-outline-orange inline-block bg-primary text-white py-3 px-4 rounded mt-1 ml-0 md:ml-6 mb-2">
              About Us
              <iconify-icon icon="tabler:arrow-right" class="inline-block ml-2"></iconify-icon>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  

  <section id="process" class="my-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">
