  <FAQs
    title="Do You have questions?"
    subtitle="The General Contractor For You"
    tagline="FAQ"
    classes={{ container: 'max-w-6xl' }}
    items={[
      {
        title: "What is your company's experience as a general contractor in Montreal?",
        description:
          "With over a decade of experience, our company has established itself as a leader in the construction sector in Montreal. We have successfully managed a multitude of projects, ranging from residential renovations to complex commercial constructions, always focusing on quality, adherence to deadlines, and customer satisfaction. Our diverse portfolio showcases our ability to meet any construction challenge.",
      },
      {
        title: "How do you guarantee the quality and compliance of the work performed?",
        description:
          "We strictly adhere to industry standards and the building codes in force in Montreal. Each project is overseen by a dedicated team of experts, including qualified project managers and specialized workers, ensuring that all work meets our high standards of quality. Additionally, we use only high-quality materials from reputable suppliers and conduct regular inspections to ensure compliance and safety.",
      },
      {
        title: "Can you provide references or examples of similar projects you have completed?",
        description:
          "Absolutely. We take pride in our accomplishments and would be delighted to share case studies and testimonials from previous projects with you. These references are available on our website or can be provided upon request. They reflect our commitment to excellence and customer satisfaction, allowing you to assess our expertise and reliability.",
      },
      {
        title: "What is the communication process during the project?",
        description:
          "Transparent and regular communication is at the heart of our approach. From the start of the project, we establish a clear communication plan, including regular updates and defined points of contact. You will have access to a dedicated project manager, available to answer all your questions and keep you informed of the progress of the work. Our goal is to ensure a stress-free experience, where your expectations are not only understood but exceeded.",
      },
      {
        title: "How do you handle unforeseen issues and changes during the project?",
        description:
          "In the construction field, flexibility is key. We have implemented robust procedures to effectively manage unforeseen issues and change requests, thus minimizing delays and additional costs. Any changes or unforeseen events are immediately communicated to the client, and options are proposed to find the best solution. Our experience allows us to anticipate and quickly resolve problems, ensuring the continuity of the project.",
      },
      {
        title: "What guarantees do you offer at the end of the work?",
        description:
          "We offer a comprehensive warranty on all our work, covering labor and materials used. This warranty is detailed in your contract and varies depending on the type of project, providing you with peace of mind long after the work is completed. In case of any issues, our team is ready to intervene quickly to perform the necessary repairs. Your satisfaction is our top priority.",
      },
    ]}
    />
    



